Name: Model Sisters
About the game: This is a game in which the photographer helps the model sisters pose correctly. In the game you act as a photographer, your model is a pair of sisters. The sisters were asked to pose in groups of mirror images. The elder sister is very professional, while the younger sister often makes the wrong moves. As a photographer, you need to point out your sister's mistakes and help her correct her posture. · Multiple scenes, free angles · Sisters wear the same costumes on the same level · Sisters will mirror pose · My sister always makes mistakes · Find sister's error and pass the level
